metadata.name: AUTUMNAL PANDEMONIUM
metadata.created_by: Susanna Rosso Wolf (SR Wolf Studio Arts)
metadata.description: AUTUMNAL PANDEMONIUM  is a 36” x 36” and 1 ¾” deep edges acrylic, oil and metallic painting on stretched cotton canvas. This abstract painting depicts the energy building during the transition period of late summer into Autumn in SW Montana.
